data.title: The Queen of Disco, Gloria Gaynor, Performed My Nightlife Baptism
data.meta_description: You might wonder why a 17-year-old would want to see a performer whose greatest hit was released the year before she was born. But "I Will Survive" is an anthem that will forever give strength to the downtrodden.
